  "proceeding": [
    {
      "background": {
        "url": "m_o1b_rain",
        "effect": ["rain"]
      }
    },
    {
      "background": {
        "url": "b_dinner_1b_rain",
        "effect": []
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "The tragedy of the first twilight was discovered at 6:00 in the morning on the following day.",
        "character": "narrator",
        "style": "replace"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": "\n\nGohda, who had woken up to get breakfast ready,",
        "character": "narrator",
        "style": "add"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " went to check on the adult siblings, who had remained in the dining hall since the previous night because of the family conference.",
        "character": "narrator",
        "style": "add"
      }
    },
    {
      "background": {
        "url": "b_1floor_s1b_rain"
      },
      "characters": {
        "middle": {
          "z-index": 1,
          "url": "c_ushiromia_battler_ub_serious_a2"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "Tell us about when you discovered the crime.",
        "character": "Battler",
        "style": "replace"
      }
    },
    {
      "background": {
        "url": "b_1floor_s1a_rain"
      },
      "characters": {
        "left": {
          "z-index": 1,
          "url": "c_gohda_goh_troubled_a2"
        },
        "middle": null
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "<purple>The dining hall was locked up.</purple>",
        "character": "Gohda",
        "style": "replace",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " Of course, there is a lock on the doors to the dining hall, but they usually remained unlocked.",
        "character": "Gohda",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "continue"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " I knocked, but there was no answer...",
        "character": "Gohda",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "characters": {
        "middle": {
          "z-index": 2,
          "url": "c_kumasawa_kum_troubled_a1"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "<purple>That's when I arrived.</purple>",
        "character": "Kumasawa",
        "style": "replace",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " I recommended that he try unlocking the door, just in case.",
        "character": "Kumasawa",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "characters": {
        "left": {
          "z-index": 1,
          "url": "c_gohda_goh_troubled_a1"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "When <purple>I unlocked the door with a master key</purple>, a terrifying sight awaited me inside...",
        "character": "Gohda",
        "style": "add"
      }
    },
    {
      "characters": {
        "middle": {
          "z-index": 2,
          "url": "c_kumasawa_kum_puzzled_a1"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "<purple>Eva-sama, Hideyoshi-sama, Rudolf-sama, Kyrie-sama, Rosa-sama, and Genji-san,</purple>",
        "character": "Kumasawa",
        "style": "replace",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": "<purple>six people in all, were lying there, covered in blood...</purple>",
        "character": "Kumasawa",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "background": {
        "url": "b_1floor_s1c_rain"
      },
      "characters": {
        "left": null,
        "middle": {
          "z-index": 1,
          "url": "c_ushiromia_krauss_uk_serious_a2"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "A great tumult followed.",
        "character": "Krauss",
        "style": "replace",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": "<purple>Everyone gathered in the dining hall.</purple>",
        "character": "Krauss",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "characters": {
        "middle": {
          "z-index": 2,
          "url": "c_ushiromia_krauss_uk_serious_a2"
        },
        "right": {
          "z-index": 1,
          "url": "c_ushiromia_natsuhi_un_puzzled_a2"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "I don't want to remember it...",
        "character": "Natsuhi",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " The sight of all the sobbing children crouched over the corpses of their own parents...",
        "character": "Natsuhi",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "background": {
        "url": "b_1floor_s1b_rain"
      },
      "characters": {
        "left": {
          "z-index": 1,
          "url": "c_ushiromia_jessica_uj_crying_a2"
        },
        "middle": null,
        "right": null
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "There was a chance they might've been alive still.",
        "character": "Jessica",
        "style": "replace",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " ...Everyone was shaking them desperately.",
        "character": "Jessica",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "characters": {
        "right": {
          "z-index": 2,
          "url": "c_shannon_sha_puzzled_a1"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "But it was no use...",
        "character": "Shannon",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": "<purple>Each of the children confirmed the deaths of their own parents...</purple>",
        "character": "Shannon",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "background": {
        "url": "b_1floor_s1a_rain"
      },
      "characters": {
        "left": {
          "z-index": 1,
          "url": "c_kanon_kan_puzzled_a2"
        },
        "right": null
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "<purple>Doctor Nanjo and I confirmed that Genji-sama was dead.</purple>",
        "character": "Kanon",
        "style": "replace"
      }
    },
    {
      "characters": {
        "right": {
          "z-index": 2,
          "url": "c_nanji_nan_troubled_a3"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "Such a gruesome way to be killed...",
        "character": "Nanjo",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": "<purple>No one is going to mistakenly confirm a death, even those other than myself.</purple>",
        "character": "Nanjo",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "characters": {
        "middle": {
          "z-index": 3,
          "url": "c_ushiromia_maria_um_evil_a1"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "It looks like <purple>all of the victims died instantly.</purple>",
        "character": "Maria",
        "style": "replace",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " ...Kihihihihi",
        "character": "Maria",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "background": {
        "url": "b_1floor_s1b_rain"
      },
      "characters": {
        "left": null,
        "middle": {
          "z-index": 2,
          "url": "c_ushiromia_krauss_uk_serious_a1"
        },
        "right": null
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "<purple>After inspecting the interior of the dining hall, we determined that all of the doors and windows had been locked, making it closed room.</purple>",
        "character": "Krauss",
        "style": "replace"
      }
    },
    {
      "characters": {
        "right": {
          "z-index": 3,
          "url": "c_ushiromia_battler_ub_troubled_a2"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "And <purple>nothing suspicious was found inside the dining hall.</purple>",
        "character": "Battler",
        "style": "replace"
      }
    },
    {
      "characters": {
        "left": {
          "z-index": 1,
          "url": "c_ushiromia_george_ug_serious_a2"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "Of course, <purple>there was no one hiding in the dining hall either.</purple>",
        "character": "George",
        "style": "add"
      }
    },
    {
      "characters": {
        "middle": {
          "z-index": 2,
          "url": "c_ushiromia_krauss_uk_worried_a1"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "Naturally.",
        "character": "Krauss",
        "style": "replace",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " All of us are here right now.",
        "character": "Krauss",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "continue"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": "<purple>It's clear that no one is hiding.</purple>",
        "character": "Krauss",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "background": {
        "url": "b_1floor_s1c_rain"
      },
      "characters": {
        "left": {
          "z-index": 1,
          "url": "c_ushiromia_jessica_uj_puzzled_a1"
        },
        "middle": null,
        "right": null
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "But Dad, if that's true, it doesn't make sense...",
        "character": "Jessica",
        "style": "replace",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " Six people were killed, and the dining hall is a closed room!",
        "character": "Jessica",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "continue"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " How could someone have killed them and escaped?!",
        "character": "Jessica",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "characters": {
        "middle": {
          "z-index": 2,
          "url": "c_ushiromia_natsuhi_un_worried_a3"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "...I'd rather not think of it,",
        "character": "Natsuhi",
        "style": "replace",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " but perhaps the servants with their master keys are the most suspicious.",
        "character": "Natsuhi",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "characters": {
        "right": {
          "z-index": 3,
          "url": "c_ushiromia_krauss_uk_serious_a1"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "They killed the six, then left and locked the door with their master keys.",
        "character": "Krauss",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " ...It is a logical theory.",
        "character": "Krauss",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "background": {
        "url": "b_1floor_s1b_rain"
      },
      "characters": {
        "left": null,
        "middle": {
          "z-index": 1,
          "url": "c_gohda_goh_troubled_a3"
        },
        "right": null
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "E-Eeek!",
        "character": "Gohda",
        "style": "replace",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " Th-That's absurd!",
        "character": "Gohda",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "background": {
        "url": "b_dinner_1b_rain",
        "effect": ["grayscale"]
      },
      "characters": {
        "middle": null
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "Since there was no chance of the culprit hiding inside the dining hall,",
        "character": "narrator",
        "style": "replace"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " it made sense to assume that the culprit locked the door after committing the murder and exiting the room.",
        "character": "narrator",
        "style": "add"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": "\n\nIt was only natural that the servants, with their master keys, would fall under suspicious.",
        "character": "narrator",
        "style": "add"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": "And, sadly enough, none of the servants had an alibi.",
        "character": "narrator",
        "style": "replace"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": "\n\nThen again, it wasn't only the servants.",
        "character": "narrator",
        "style": "add"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " Everyone else lacked an alibi as well.",
        "character": "narrator",
        "style": "add"
      }
    },
    {
      "background": {
        "url": "b_different_space_1a",
        "effect": []
      },
      "characters": {
        "right": {
          "z-index": 2,
          "url": "c_ushiromia_battler_cape_ubc_oh_a1"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "Is there any way to lock up from the outside without a master key?",
        "character": "Battler",
        "style": "replace"
      }
    },
    {
      "characters": {
        "left": {
          "z-index": 1,
          "url": "c_bernkastel_ber_apathy_a2"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "No, there isn't.",
        "character": "Bernkastel",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " ......Hmm, that's not enough.",
        "character": "Bernkastel",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "continue"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " I'll say it with the red truth.",
        "character": "Bernkastel",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "background": {
        "url": "black"
      },
      "characters": {
        "left": null,
        "right": null
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "<red>All doors can only be locked or unlocked with a master key.</red>",
        "character": "narrator",
        "style": "replace"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": "\n\n<red>Of course, it is possible to lock or unlock the doors from inside the room even without a master key.</red>",
        "character": "narrator",
        "style": "add"
      }
    },
    {
      "background": {
        "url": "b_different_space_1a"
      },
      "characters": {
        "left": {
          "z-index": 1,
          "url": "c_lambdadelta_lam_indulgent_a3"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "There you have it.",
        "character": "Lambdadelta",
        "style": "replace",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " Any other questions?",
        "character": "Lambdadelta",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "characters": {
        "right": {
          "z-index": 2,
          "url": "c_beatrice_bea_serious_a2"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "Shouldn't there be keys to each individual room, in addition to the master keys?",
        "character": "Beatrice",
        "style": "add"
      }
    },
    {
      "background": {
        "url": "b_different_space_1b"
      },
      "characters": {
        "left": null,
        "right": {
          "z-index": 2,
          "url": "c_bernkastel_ber_apathy_a1"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "...Normally, those would exist.",
        "character": "Bernkastel",
        "style": "replace",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " However, they make the game more complicated, so I've eliminated them.",
        "character": "Bernkastel",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "continue"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " Red truth.",
        "character": "Bernkastel",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "continue"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": "<red>We'll consider master keys to be the only keys that exist.</red>",
        "character": "Bernkastel",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "characters": {
        "left": {
          "z-index": 1,
          "url": "c_ushiromia_battler_cape_ubc_scowl_a1"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "In other words,",
        "character": "Battler",
        "style": "replace",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " all of the locks that appear in this game can only be locked or unlocked by master keys.",
        "character": "Battler",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "background": {
        "url": "b_different_space_1a"
      },
      "characters": {
        "left": null,
        "right": {
          "z-index": 2,
          "url": "c_lambdadelta_lam_evil_a1"
        }
      },
      "text": {
        "content": "That's what it means.",
        "character": "Lambdadelta",
        "style": "replace",
        "statement": "start"
      }
    },
    {
      "text": {
        "content": " It really is a simple game.",
        "character": "Lambdadelta",
        "style": "add",
        "statement": "end"
      }
    },
    {
      "characters": {
        "left": {
          "z-index": 1,
          "url": "c_beatrice_bea_apathy_a1"
        }
      },
      "text": {
